<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-95-0980 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book presents papers on tungsten and other refractory metals forVLSI applications. Topics include the following: Selectivity loss andnucleation on insulators, fundamental reaction and growth studies, chemicalvapor deposition of tungsten, chemical vapor deposition of molybdenum,reactive ion etching of refractory metal films; and properties of refractorymetals deposited by sputtering.</TEXT></DOC>